node.text:
At a very early age, I realized the importance of focusing on the thing I can always 100% control. 
The effort I put in with my own two hands. 
My word is in my handshake. 
My work ethic is in callouses. 
My gratitude and humility is in my scars. 
You want to know me? 
Shake my hand and you’ll know my story. 
Then if I really like you we’ll have some Teremana tequila 🥃 😉 and have some real fun. 
Our 2019 comes to a grateful close and lets embrace 2020 with relentless passion. 
#twohandphilosophy

@therock you made a big impact on my life, and you are a big inspiration to me and you’ve helped me get through things I couldn’t get through just by listening to what you say thank you so much Dwayne/therock!🙏🏼
You are an inspiration too... A good man we look up to and admire!!! Thankyou for being you and paving the way for men to follow and become gentlemen and heroes.  World needs more @therock. 🙌😊❤️
This is a lovely pic of you!  I’m sorry to hear your hands were hurt.  Hope you are okay now.
We should be friends but i feel you are way to cool to be my friend 😂 and rich and mich more inlike me hahaha
